      • onComplete

        void onComplete​(@NonNull
                java.lang.String originalFile,
                java.lang.String newFile,
                int status,
                java.lang.String reason)
        Callback method that is always called when the image action is completed.
        Parameters:
        originalFile - the path to the original file
        newFile - the path to the file that has been actioned or null if cancelled or failure has occurred.
        status - one of ACTION_SUCCESS, ACTION_FAILURE, ACTION_CANCELLED
        reason - any human readable text that helps the user understand the reason for a failure
